collection.description:
YBCC is a premium club that consist of 9,999 YOLO Bunnies - music artists & lovers that traveled across a wormhole from the No. 1,402 universe. 

It is exclusively for its members and will grant benefits to them in special days.  The benefits will include platform token airdrop, plots airdrop and the only chance to receive the genesis headphone NFT which will initiate the L2E (Listen to Earn)etc. Future areas and perks can be unlocked by the community with the development of Muverse.
